# snake-game

Snake game, made with python & curses. Play in the terminal. For Linux, Mac OS and Windows.

<p align="center">
  <img src="doc/screenshot.png" />
</p>

## How to install

```shell
$ pip install snake-game
```

## How to play

```shell
$ snake
```

